2.00	Arto_salomaa	Arto Salomaa	Arto Salomaa (born 6 June 1934) is a Finnish mathematician and computer scientist. His research career, which spans over forty years, is focused on formal languages and automata theory. A 2004 citation stated that "Arto is without doubt the founder of automata and formal language theory in Europe".	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/C04_0272-ArtoSalomaa.edited.jpg/170px-C04_0272-ArtoSalomaa.edited.jpg
